title: Irupathiyonnam noottandu
subTitle: Appu, a restaurateur and surfer based in Goa, falls in love with Zaya. When she goes back home to Kerala, Appu takes it upon himself to find her and confess his feelings.

title: Swathanthryam Ardharathriyil
subTitle: Jacob, a manager at a major financial firm, is arrested while trying to save the woman he loves from a criminal case. In prison, he befriends fellow inmates, and together they devise a plan to escape.

title: Kili Poyi
subTitle: Friends Chacko and Hari are fed up with their employer and plan a trip to Goa. Their trip turns into something unusual when they discover a mysterious bag.

title: Koode
subTitle: Following the loss of his sister, a young man is forced to reflect on his childhood and reassess his future. However, he finds support and courage from unexpected quarters.

title: Njandukalude Nattil Oridavela
subTitle: Kurian, a naive man, visits home from London expecting for his nuptials. Later, he learns about his mother's cancer and supports her through the treatment.

title: Summer in Bethlehem
subTitle: Ravishankar pretends to own the farmhouse of his friend Dennis when his relatives pay a visit along with their granddaughters. Chaos ensues after his prospective bride confesses her love for Dennis.

title: Sreekrishnapurathe Nakshathrathilakkam
subTitle: Three out of four brothers of a Malayali household are happily married while the fourth brother is engaged. When the beautiful Yamuna Rani becomes their new neighbour, she poses a threat to the wives.

title: Trance
subTitle: Viju, a motivational speaker, is hired to be the face of a religious scam for which he undergoes rigorous training. As his popularity grows, he sinks into the depths of darkness and delusion.

title: Marakkar Arabikkadalinte Simham
subTitle: The naval chieftain of the Zamorin of Calicut, Kunjali Marakkar IV, develops a highly-equipped naval defence to fight against the Portuguese invaders in India.

title: Salala Mobiles
subTitle: A young mobile phone shop owner's life takes a turn after he gets his hands on a tapping app. Meanwhile, his heart finds comfort in the presence of a beautiful woman waiting at a bus stand nearby.

title: Salala Mobiles
subTitle: A young mobile phone shop owner's life takes a turn after he gets his hands on a tapping app. Meanwhile, his heart finds comfort in the presence of a beautiful woman waiting at a bus stand nearby.

title: Sooryan
subTitle: Sooryan aspires to follow in the footsteps of his father and become a singer. However, he realises that his journey to stardom will be filled with hurdles because of his father's debts.

title: Irul
subTitle: Alex and Archana go on a trip but soon their car breaks down, and they take shelter at a nearby house. However, things take a turn when the owner of the house behaves in a suspicious manner.

title: Mayookham
subTitle: Unni Kesavan's carefree and rebellious life is challenged when childhood friend Indira returns, bringing warmth, reflection and a chance for personal growth.

title: Pachakuthira
subTitle: Anandakkuttan's life as a young artist takes a dramatic turn when he takes his autistic brother under his wing, leading to an unexpected yet heartwarming bond between them.

title: China Town
subTitle: Mathukutty, Zachariah and Binoy, whose fathers were friends twenty years ago, return to Goa in order to reclaim a casino. But they face many challenges when a local goon tries to plot against them.

title: Bromance
subTitle: When Binto learns of his brother Shinto's disappearance, his search for Shinto leads him to collaborate with others, resulting in unforeseen turns, revelations, and memorable experiences.

title: Kantara
subTitle: When greed paves the way for betrayal, scheming and murder, a young tribal reluctantly dons the traditions of his ancestors to seek justice.

title: Udayananu Tharam
subTitle: A struggling director gets cheated by his friend who steals his script and becomes a famous actor. However, when he finally gets the chance to direct a film, he is forced to cast a dubious actor.

title: Masters
subTitle: Milan Paul and Sreeramakrishnan are very good friends and always help each other out. They soon try to unravel the mystery behind a series of murders and suicides that hits the town.

title: Masters
subTitle: Milan Paul and Sreeramakrishnan are very good friends and always help each other out. They soon try to unravel the mystery behind a series of murders and suicides that hits the town.

title: Veeralipattu
subTitle: Harinarayanan, a young man who works in Chennai, is in love with Pooja, the daughter of a rich couple. However, he and his family are forced to bear the burden of tradition.

title: Nayattu
subTitle: Three police officers go on the run after being framed for a crime by corrupt officials. Against the backdrop of dirty politics and bureaucracy, they strive to avoid being arrested.

title: Nanma
subTitle: For a living, Muthu extracts and disposes of corpses from rivers. Unknown to Muthu, his son becomes a henchman for a moneylender as he wants his father to have a respectable job.

title: Pullippulikalum Aattinkuttiyum
subTitle: Gopan, a tourist guide, issues a statement against his rival, Kuriyachan, regarding a human trafficking case. However, Kuriyachan seeks revenge against Gopan.

title: Avatharam
subTitle: Kuppaswamy, an innocent theatre enthusiast, falls in love with visually challenged Ponnama after joining a troupe. When the troupe struggles financially, the couple moves to the city.

title: Kilichundan Mambazham
subTitle: Moidukutty Haji returns to his village after taking a third wife, despite his other wives' disapproval. Unbeknownst to him, his young and beautiful new bride, Amina, is secretly in love with Abdu, a bangle seller.

title: Puthan Panam
subTitle: Nityananda Shenoy, a gangster from Kasaragod, decides to exact revenge on an ex-minister who swindled him right before demonetisation. Meanwhile, Muthuvel and his mother struggle to survive in Kochi.

title: Ittymaani: Made in China
subTitle: Ittymaani, who was raised in China, runs a business of counterfeit products in India. However, when he tries to help Annamma who is ignored by her sons, he lands in trouble because she falls ill.

title: YSR Yatra
subTitle: A renowned Indian politician embarks on a 900-mile walking tour and interacts with his followers as part of his election campaign.
